\section{Fabrication}
We characterize 3 samples: TM amorphous Silicon strip and TE-TM regular Silicon strips. Amorphous Silicon samples started from silicon‑-on‑-insulator (SOI) wafers with 220nm Si thickness. After growing 253nm amorphous silicon waveguides were etched. We measured 4dB/cm propagation losses through different length waveguides.

